  "recipeInstructions": "1. Preheat oven to 350°F.\n2. Mix all ingredients thoroughly.\n3. Place spoonfuls of the mixture on a cookie sheet.\n4. Bake for 12 to 14 minutes.\n5. Makes 4 dozen cookies. These freeze well.",
